in fiscal 2003, the company sold the anaheim
angels baseball team, which resulted in a pre-tax gain of
$16million. in fiscal 2002, the company sold the disney
store operations in japan generating a pre-tax gain of
$34million and in fiscal 2001, the company sold infoseek
japan k.k. generating a $22million pre-tax gain. these
gains are reported in the line gain on sale of
businesses in the consolidated statements of income.
