table of contents
the companys leveraged lease investment
includes the impact of certain income tax benefits that are
projected to be realized in the future under the current u.s.
income tax laws. as discussed more fully in note8, the
u.s. congress is considering a change in the applicable income
tax law. since the impact of this matter upon the company
depends upon the specific provisions of any tax legislation
ultimately enacted by congress, it is not possible to predict
the impact on our results of operations or financial position.
